{"tid":1033137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"車牌可以加入表情符號 澳洲昆士蘭創新作法3月上路","createTime":"2019-02-23T01:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T05:51:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f8a0a0f72db06448246ebf9dddaff3154543aa4","tid":1033137,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpuvZhkv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpuvZhkv.jpg&h=f9ba70cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳州昆士蘭州政府更宣布，3月1日將為居民提供表情符號車牌。（圖擷自IG）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-22 16:13<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕隨著現代人漸漸習慣用傳訊息代替打電話，很多人開始會用表情符號（emojis）代替文字。現在澳州昆士蘭州政府更宣布，3月1日將為居民提供表情符號車牌。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，澳洲昆士蘭州政府從3月1日將為當地居民提供帶有表情符號的車牌，不過目前還不允許車牌上完全只使用表情符號，最少還是要有2個字母、2個數字的組合。此外，現在也僅開放5種最「正面」的表情符號，分別是笑臉、愛心眼、哭笑不得、眨眼、戴太陽眼鏡笑臉。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友都對於這樣的創新作法感到新奇，「這個我喜歡。」、「太酷了。」、「超有創意的。」但也有網友幽默表示，未來警察在追逃犯時，必須這樣講，「我們在追捕一台紅色Toyota Prius，車牌是X-5-M-4-X-眨眼表情，嫌犯有武器而且十分危險。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2706830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2706830&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1GL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=3f3e19a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2706830&h=aadf95c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2706830</a>"},{"pid":"89ddcb83375c61ae4a7f92f475a99081da74d879","tid":1033137,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />